Text: Re FW Pipeline HistoricalsI am forwarding your request on to Lori Creer Her phone She should be able to respond to your request Jerry Gross Questar Pipeline Company Smith Matt AM Jerry I requested some questar flow historicals from you per the following email I am still in need of the referenced data and would appreciate an indication of when it will be provided If you have any questions feel free to contact me at the number below Thank you Mathew Smith Original Message From Smith Matt Sent Thursday April PM To Subject Pipeline Historicals Gerry Per our conversation I am requesting historical scheduled final cycle quantities for Questar Pipeline meter points Questar previously provided flows up to June of We are now requesting from June to March I would prefer the information be emailed to me Otherwise the postal address is RmE Smith St Houston TX Please feel free to contact me with any questions at Thank you Mathew Smith
